    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1868-07-13T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1868-07-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="423" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d423">
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Señor Benitez</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr. Washburn</persName>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Ministry of State for Foreign
                                            Affairs,</hi>
                            <hi rend="italic">Luque,</hi>
                        </placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-07-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">July</hi> 13, 1868.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Again called upon by the judicial authorities, I beg your excellency
                                will excuse me for molesting you once more, to request you to
                                dismiss from your hotel the North American citizen Porter Cornelius
                                Bliss, and the British subject George Masterman, accused of crimes
                                not less grave than the others whose dismissal I have already had
                                the honor to request.</p>
                <p>I embrace this occasion to renew to your excellency the assurances of
                                my distinguished consideration and esteem.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>GUMESINDO BENITEZ.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>His Excellency <hi rend="smallcaps">Charles A. Washburn</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Minister Resident of the United States of
                                        America.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
